data.description: Located in Southeast Boise this move-in ready home has no HOAs and is situated near schools, parks, and downtown. Inside find recently refinished floors, new carpet in the front living room and large windows allowing in ample natural light. The kitchen has been recently updated with new tile, granite countertops and fixtures and features a breakfast bar. Downstairs you will find a large second living area as well as a bedroom and full bathroom. Upstairs is an additional bedroom and the primary bedroom that has an additional entrance into the large bathroom. Sliding glass doors take you out to the backyard deck perfect for BBQs and entertaining. The backyard has mature landscaping and an area for a garden. With multiple sheds, a two car garage, and RV parking you will find room for all your toys and storage needs!
